@Roland 

By my count, IVEY has been clued to the poker player three times, beginning in 2009. Today is the first appearance of PHIL IVEY. 

I needed a few crosses to get that answer.

@Mean Old Lady " if we had mutilated a POTATO there would have been....um, consequences."

I think that the point was that the primary child-rearing parent (assumed to be [Palindromic family member], natch) would lend the children a potato, and when playtime was over, Mrs. Potato Head would be retrieved, scrubbed, and transmogrified into Pommes de Terre Duchesse.

IMO, once Hasbro started including those plastic "potatoes" with the pre-assigned holes, the experience was ruined, sapped of all creativity, all joy.  Well, that and I grew up.

